[{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/comments/853436606","html_url":"https://github.com/libgdx/libgdx/issues/6552#issuecomment-853436606","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/6552","id":853436606,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDg1MzQzNjYwNg==","user":{"login":"tommyettinger","id":160684,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE2MDY4NA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/160684?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger","html_url":"https://github.com/tommyettinger","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2021-06-02T23:00:56Z","updated_at":"2021-06-02T23:00:56Z","body":"I'm working on this now; I can absolutely reproduce the issue. The exact conditions for when the wrapping bug occurs are... strange. It shows up when it uses the specific scaling factor you had, `14 / font.getCapHeight()`, or `0.5185185f`, but not `0.5f` or `0.625f`.\r\n\r\n0.625f:\r\n\r\n![0.625f](https://i.imgur.com/aIsdx0C.png)\r\n\r\n0.5185185f:\r\n\r\n![0.5185185f](https://i.imgur.com/0PKTJ7k.png)\r\n\r\n0.5f:\r\n\r\n![0.5f](https://i.imgur.com/M03SXY5.png)\r\n\r\nI have a tentative fix, but I don't know if it breaks anything else yet. It simply changes, in GlyphLayout.java and its `setText()` method:\r\n```java\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\tGlyph glyph = run.glyphs.get(i - 1);\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\tfloat glyphWidth = (glyph.width + glyph.xoffset) * fontData.scaleX - fontData.padRight;\r\n```\r\nto\r\n```java\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\tfloat glyphWidth = xAdvances[i-1];\r\n```","author_association":"MEMBER","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/comments/853436606/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"tommyettinger","id":160684,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE2MDY4NA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/160684?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger","html_url":"https://github.com/tommyettinger","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tommyettinger/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/comments/853437992","html_url":"https://github.com/libgdx/libgdx/issues/6552#issuecomment-853437992","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/libgdx/libgdx/issues/6552","id":853437992,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDg1MzQzNzk5Mg==","user":{"login":"tommyettinger","id":160684,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE2MDY4NA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/160684?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomm